bud
===

author: Peter Hoffmann

Overview
--------

bud runs stuff for you

Installation / Usage
--------------------

To install use pip:

    $ pip install bud


Or clone the repo:

    $ git clone https://github.com/hoffmann/bud.git
    $ python setup.py install

